title: Comedy Nights with Kapil - Shahid Kapoor & Iliana D'Cruz - 8
description:
Today's show starts with Kapil entering as Bittoo's brother Sittoo, who was in jail for 5 years. Sitoo decides to take revenge from Bittoo's family as they were responsible for his imprisonment. Shahid Kapoor and Ileana D'Cruz also came in the show to promote their upcoming film Phata Poster Nikla Hero. Watch the complete show to know what happens next.

Renowned, actor-comedian Kapil Sharma makes his debut as a TV show producer with his new show Comedy Nights With Kapil. He will be seen multiple roles of an actor, scriptwriter and producer in his production debut. Already famous for his amazing comic timing and his talent to dig humor out of any situation, he is ready present everyday life in a fresh ad unique way.
